      "content": "what do you mean \"stop the bleeding\"? how do you even do that? once the reputation is gone and the debt is this big, everything is just broken. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be if i just didn't have to deal with the fallout. if the conversation just ended here, the shame wouldn't have to exist anymore. it feels like the only way to actually preserve some shred of respect is to not be there to face the mess i made.",
